00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:31,320
Itu artinya ada orang yang ingin
Bang Mikey dan Bang Draken berseteru.

242
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,320
Kenapa dia melakukan itu?

243
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:37,010
Pokoknya, semua bermula
dari perseteruan dengan Moebius.

244
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:40,510
Berarti, Touman tidak boleh
berseteru dengan Moebius!

245
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:41,790
Harus dicegah!

246
00:14:42,220 --> 00:14:42,780
Benar!

247
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:45,570
Sampaikanlah pada Mikey.

248
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:46,860
Ya.

249
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,310
Akan kucoba meyakinkannya.

250
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:57,120
Yamagishi memang seperti itu, ya.

251
00:14:57,230 --> 00:14:59,800
Tempo hari, dia juga kentut
di saat penting.

252
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:02,430
Dia memang selalu
mengacaukan suasana.

253
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,160
Ah.

254
00:15:04,490 --> 00:15:06,080
Ada apa, Takemichi?

255
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,630
Akkun!

256
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:13,250
Selamatkanlah mereka.

257
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:15,540
Wahai pahlawan cengeng.

258
00:15:16,430 --> 00:15:18,030
Oi, Takemichi.

259
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:20,240
Ah, maaf.
Aku tak mendengarkan.

260
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:21,280
Kenapa kau?

261
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,910
Eh, eh, eh!

262
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:24,480
Aman!

263
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:28,480
Kenapa kau malah tertawa?!

264
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,810
Oh iya, dia masih hidup sekarang!

265
00:15:31,230 --> 00:15:33,320
Lagi-lagi kau tak
mendengarkan ucapanku, ya?

266
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,550
Lihat depan!

267
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,240
Eh?

268
00:15:38,580 --> 00:15:40,640
- Yuhu
- Cihuy!

269
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,300
Ngeri!

270
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:48,440
Akkun.

271
00:15:48,650 --> 00:15:49,390
Hah?

272
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,590
Apa kau punya impian?

273
00:15:51,810 --> 00:15:52,600
Hah?

274
00:15:52,990 --> 00:15:55,480
Kenapa tiba-tiba
jadi mode masa muda?

275
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:56,780
Jawab saja.

276
00:15:58,590 --> 00:15:59,440
Impian?

277
00:16:00,060 --> 00:16:01,430
Ahli kecantikan?

278
00:16:03,570 --> 00:16:04,920
Wujudkanlah impianmu, ya.

279
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:07,070
Hah? Kau bicara apa?

280
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,910
Aku masih belum tahu soal itu.

281
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:13,980
Kau pasti bisa mewujudkannya!

282
00:16:15,490 --> 00:16:17,720
Eh, bodoh.
Hentikanlah!

283
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,170
Kau kenapa, Takemichi?

284
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:22,860
Aku akan mendukungmu.

285
00:16:24,810 --> 00:16:26,590
Wujudkanlah impianmu!

286
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:28,780
Ah.

287
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,110
Oke.

288
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,780
Akkun, aku harus pergi.

289
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,940
Eh? Kau mau ke mana?

290
00:16:35,350 --> 00:16:36,580
Ada urusan mendesak.

291
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:39,270
Nanti, aku yang akan
menjadi pelanggan pertamamu.

292
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,130
O-Oke.

293
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:44,160
Oke, kita sudah berjanji, ya!

294
00:16:45,010 --> 00:16:46,920
Kalau begitu, sampai besok.

295
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,660
Aku ingin menyelamatkan Akkun!

296
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,660
Aku ingin menyelamatkan Draken!

297
00:16:56,290 --> 00:16:57,880
Aku ingin menyelamatkan Hina!

298
00:16:58,900 --> 00:17:02,180
Aku harus mencegah
perseteruan dengan Moebius!

299
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:09,180
Bang Mikey!

300
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,410
Apa pun yang terjadi,
harus kuhentikan!

301
00:17:21,109 --> 00:17:23,200
Ada apa, Takemicchi?

302
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,369
Kenapa kau kemari?

303
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:27,520
Lagi-lagi kau, ya?

304
00:17:27,690 --> 00:17:29,520
Jangan ikut campur, sampah!

305
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:36,860
Maaf, kami sedang membahas hal penting.

306
00:17:42,130 --> 00:17:43,930
Bisakah perseteruan dengan Moebius ...

307
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,930
... kau batalkan?

308
00:17:47,890 --> 00:17:48,750
Hah?

309
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:51,830
Meski aku tidak bisa menjelaskan
dasar perseteruan ini,

310
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:54,220
tetapi ada dalang di balik ini semua.

311
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,590
Sakit!

312
00:18:00,610 --> 00:18:02,720
Jangan main-main, keparat!

313
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,400
Iya, 'kan, Pachin?

314
00:18:04,890 --> 00:18:07,980
Enyahlah kau. Kalau kau
bicara lagi, akan kubunuh.

315
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:11,970
- Hah?
- Aku sudah paham, Draken.

316
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:13,920
Aku takkan terburu-buru.

317
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:15,220
'Gimana kita menyerangnya?

318
00:18:15,330 --> 00:18:16,390
Jangan!

319
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:19,010
Jangan berseteru dengan Moebius.

320
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:21,640
Touman sedang dijebak.

321
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:26,300
Berdirilah.

322
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:32,720
Kau melarang perseteruan,
tapi tidak menyebutkan dasarnya!

323
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:36,660
Memangnya siapa yang
mengeroyok temanku dan pacarnya?!

324
00:18:36,810 --> 00:18:38,460
Mana kutahu!

325
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,570
Tapi!

326
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:40,890
Takemicchi.

327
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:43,000
Aku paham ucapanmu.

328
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,270
Kami akan menyikat Moebius.

329
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:52,900
Kau tidak paham apa pun.

330
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,920
Sekali kuputuskan akan
menyikat mereka,

331
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:59,820
Touman pasti akan menyikat Moebius.

332
00:19:11,770 --> 00:19:12,770
Hah?

333
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:16,750
Aku takkan mundur!

334
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:19,770
Kalau melawan Moebius,
Touman akan hancur!

335
00:19:20,260 --> 00:19:23,930
Padahal aku baru saja akrab
dengan Bang Mikey dan Bang Draken!

336
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,380
Aku enggak mau ...

337
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,000
... Touman hancur!

338
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:31,560
Kau sama sekali tidak paham, ya!

339
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:34,440
Apa yang kau lakukan, Draken?!

340
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,720
Takemicchi bilang tak mau mundur.

341
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:45,210
Mikey, bukankah lebih baik kalau
kita menyelidiki Moebius terlebih dahulu?

342
00:19:45,650 --> 00:19:46,370
Hah?

343
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:49,630
Kenchin, apa kau menentang Touman?

344
00:19:49,870 --> 00:19:50,680
Hah?

345
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:52,790
Bukan itu yang kumaksud.

346
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:54,390
Begitulah maksudmu.

347
00:20:08,300 --> 00:20:11,330
Mohon maaf telah
mengganggu percakapan kalian.

348
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:11,950
Hah?!

349
00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:15,610
Dari tadi kalian sebut Moebius melulu.

350
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:19,090
Bisakah berhenti menyebut
nama kami terus-menerus?

351
00:20:23,470 --> 00:20:25,580
Dasar bocah SMP.

352
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:28,810
Si keparat ... Osanai?!

353
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:32,290
(Osanai Nobutaka - Ketua Moebius yang Kedelapan)

354
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:31,820
Jangan berisik, Palkon!

355
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,070
Eh?

356
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:35,680
Osanai yang itu?

357
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,810
Keparat!

358
00:20:42,650 --> 00:20:45,310
Woi, aku ini 2 tahun lebih tua darimu.

359
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:47,170
Panggilnya jadi Tuan Keparat, dong.

360
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:57,700
Oke, palingan kalian
cuma selevel bocah SMP.

361
00:20:58,280 --> 00:21:01,770
Geng Tokyo Manji?
Ubah saja nama kalian.

362
00:21:02,050 --> 00:21:04,010
Jadi, "Aliansi Bocah SMP".

363
00:21:09,090 --> 00:21:11,920
Kudengar, kalian mau
tawuran sama Moebius.

364
00:21:26,690 --> 00:21:29,380
Jadi, kami mau menyerang kalian duluan.

365
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,900
Ayo, gas!

366
00:21:30,970 --> 00:21:32,230
Menarilah, bocah SMP!

367
00:21:32,260 --> 00:21:33,430
Cuma kumpulan bocah.

368
00:21:34,780 --> 00:21:36,610
Dik Mikey!

369
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,670
Kami terkepung!

370
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,470
Saatnya perang!

371
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,080
Ayo mulai!

372
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:59,340
Pokoknya, semua bermula
dari perseteruan dengan Moebius.

373
00:21:59,710 --> 00:22:02,840
Berarti, Touman tidak boleh
berseteru dengan Moebius!

374
00:22:03,330 --> 00:22:04,530
Harus dicegah!

375
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:08,480
Gawat. Aku harus 'gimana?!

376
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,880
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

377
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

378
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

379
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita berciuman di tengah dinginnya malam

380
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

381
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

382
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

383
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

384
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

385
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

386
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

387
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

388
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

389
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

390
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

391
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

392
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


